text: Þis synt þa landgemæra to Stantune.
Ærest on wynlmæddune west heafod<../images/tbar.gif>on þa ealdan dic.
Þanne of þære byrig þweofer þane sceagan.
Þonne forð a be wyrit truman<../images/tbar.gif>on wodnes dic.
Þanne of wodnes dic on þa byrug norðewearde andlang gemæres<../images/tbar.gif>innan corsan.
<../images/tbar.gif>west andlanges herpaðes<../images/tbar.gif>eft on wulmæddune west heafod.
Þonne is binnan þam tyn hydun ælfsiges þridde healfe hide.
